tool_description: Provides geo location and information about countries and cities
title: Countries Cities

api_list.name: Cities in the Country

api_list.name: Country GeoJson
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://countries-cities.p.rapidapi.com/location/country/{code}/geojson"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "countries-cities.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
